      • LineMarkerInfo

        public LineMarkerInfo(T element,
                      TextRange range,
                      javax.swing.Icon icon,
                      Function<? super T,java.lang.String> tooltipProvider,
                      GutterIconNavigationHandler<T> navHandler,
                      GutterIconRenderer.Alignment alignment)
        Creates a line marker info for the element. See LineMarkerProvider.getLineMarkerInfo(PsiElement) javadoc for specific quirks on which elements to use for line markers.
        Parameters:
        element - the element for which the line marker is created.
        range - the range (relative to beginning of file) with which the marker is associated
        icon - the icon to show in the gutter for the line marker
        tooltipProvider - the callback to calculate the tooltip for the gutter icon
        navHandler - the handler executed when the gutter icon is clicked
